data.description: Enchantment awaits where panoramic Columbia River views take center stage and Bohemian charm meets modern living. The main floor welcomes you with a unique local artist designed kitchen, cozy bedroom, convenient bathroom, and a sun room boasting a rustic wood stove. Your perfect retreat for relaxation. Ascend to the upper level, where three additional bedrooms await. Experience breathtaking river views from the rooftop, offering an enchanting escape right at your doorstep. Unwind in the second bathroom, adorned with cheerful custom tile. Venture into the backyard to discover the secret garden, a tranquil oasis just waiting to be your personal sanctuary. The basement provides ample storage space for all your needs, and could be a perfect spot for an artist nook. The convenient location of this extraordinary residence places you in close proximity to downtown Astoria, where an array of charming shops, restaurants, and amenities await your exploration. Whether you're drawn to the river's tranquility or the vibrant pulse of Astoria, this residence offers the best of both worlds. This distinctive property is a rare find, offering a lifestyle that's truly one-of-a-kind.
